We will write a Python script to sort these words alphabetically.

```python
# List of words to be sorted
words = ["keller", "frame", "hippodrome", "bungle", "yolk", "anheuser", "prompt", "together", "spidery", "chaperon", "miterwort"]

# Sorting the list alphabetically
sorted_words = sorted(words)

# Output the sorted list
print(sorted_words)
```
